Goddy Egene Trancorp Hotels Plc has launched a new platform, Aura, that connects people to great accommodation, great food, and memorable experiences in different cities across Africa. According to the Managing Director/CEO of Transcorp Hotels Plc, Dupe Olusola, “It is a new dawn in the hospitality industry. I am thrilled to introduce you to Aura by Transcorp, the digital platform we are using to connect people to quality accommodation, great food, and awesome experiences.”